{"word":"Spirituality","slug":"spirituality","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Spirituality</b> Described as the great and enduring good<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=10&verse=42'>Luk 10:42</a><br/> Described as love and devotion to God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=6&verse=5'>Deu 6:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=22&verse=5'>Jos 22:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=8&verse=23'>1Ki 8:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=1&verse=2'>Psa 1:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=51&verse=6'>Psa 51:6</a><br/> Brings peace<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=26&verse=3'>Isa 26:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=33&verse=6'>Jer 33:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=8&verse=6'>Rom 8:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=14&verse=17'>Rom 14:17</a><br/> Brings indifference to worldly good<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=7&verse=31'>1Co 7:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=3&verse=3'>Col 3:3</a><br/> Brings thirst for heavenly blessings<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=5&verse=6'>Mat 5:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=6&verse=27'>Joh 6:27</a><br/> Is produced by the indwelling of the Holy Spirit<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=14&verse=17'>Joh 14:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=8&verse=4'>Rom 8:4</a>"}]}